{"type":"message","id":"655255ae","parentId":"9e861afe","timestamp":"2026-05-30T09:17:58.707Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ed7821de48984fa296369f9d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Speed 测试开发文档\n\n## 概述\n\nSpeed测试用于测量PTZ设备在不同速度等级下的实际移动速度。\n\n---\n\n## 更新纪要\n\n### 2026-05-30 修复 Pan 无限位和 Tilt 翻转问题\n\n**问题**：\n1. Pan 无限位时起点位置错误，从当前位置开始导致跳变后继续测试时位置混乱\n2. Pan 无限位距离计算错误，跳变数据被排除或计算不准确\n3. Tilt 到达限位后继续采样，设备反向移动的数据被记录\n4. Tilt 翻转检测不触发，停在 900 时趋势和为 0\n\n**修复**：\n\n#### 1. Pan 无限位起点逻辑\n- 使用虚拟限位：min=10, max=3590\n- 根据 `direction_info` 确定起点：\n  - `positive_command_increases=false`, `direction=1` → start=3590\n  - `positive_command_increases=false`, `direction=-1` → start=10\n\n#### 2. Pan 无限位距离计算\n- 检测跳变点：相邻两点差值 > 1800\n- 分段计算距离（绝对值）：\n  - 跳变前：abs(起点 - 0)\n  - 跳变后：abs(3600 - 终点)\n- 累加各段距离\n\n#### 3. Tilt 停止逻辑\n- 条件1：达到限位20点持续 tmin/tmax\n- 条件2：连续5个点数值降低\n- 两个条件满足任意一个立即停止\n\n#### 4. 到达限位后立即停止\n- 删除采样额外5个点的逻辑\n- 避免设备反向移动的数据被记录\n\n#### 5. 后处理最小数据量\n- 降低最小数据量要求：110点 → 20点\n\n---\n\n## TODO 待修复清单\n\n| # | 问题 | 当前逻辑 | 正确逻辑 | 状态 |\n|---|------|----------|----------|------|\n| 1 | 测试顺序错误 | 同方向走3次 → 换方向走3次 | 正向反向交替，重复3次 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 2 | 速度计算时间写死 | `len(valid) * 0.1` | 用时间戳计算实际时间 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 3 | 测试结束后未验证稳定 | `stop_move()` + `sleep(2)` | `stop_move()` + 验证20点稳定 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 4 | 后处理未使用时间戳 | 只读 position | 读 timestamp + position | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 5 | Tilt轴翻转检测逻辑 | 检测900±200范围内递减 | 连续5点递减 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 6 | Pan轴有限位时起止位置 | 已有逻辑 | 根据 positive_command_increases 确定起点 | ✅ 已实现 |\n| 7 | Pan轴无限位起点 | `start_pos = None` | 虚拟限位 min=10, max=3590 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 8 | Pan轴无限位距离计算 | 净位移或排除跳变 | 分段计算，绝对值累加 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 9 | Tilt到达限位后继续采样 | 采样5个点 | 立即停止 | ✅ 已修复 |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780132678707}}
{"type":"message","id":"640c2505","parentId":"655255ae","timestamp":"2026-05-30T09:18:03.552Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-560a64d88bf1488cbcf23feb4aee075b","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\speed.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":19523,"output":32,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19555,"cost":{"input":0.019523,"output":0.00010240000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.019625399999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780132678708,"responseId":"cht000d1c76@dx19e782d0d77b8aa822"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f75cbc23","parentId":"640c2505","timestamp":"2026-05-30T09:18:03.589Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-560a64d88bf1488cbcf23feb4aee075b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\r\nAstroHub v2.0 - 速度测试模块 (Speed Testing)\r\n\r\n实现速度测试:\r\n- measure_speed_single: 单点速度测量\r\n- post_process_csv: 数据后处理\r\n- run_all_tests: 完整测试流程\r\n\r\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\r\n\"\"\"\r\n\r\nfrom __future__ import annotations\r\n\r\nimport csv\r\nimport time\r\nfrom datetime import datetime\r\nfrom pathlib import Path\r\nfrom typing import Any\r\n\r\nfrom src.advanced.device_path import get_device_info, get_data_path_read, get_data_path_write\r\nfrom src.advanced.device_config import get_current_device, set_current_device, update_device_info\r\n\r\ndef _print(msg: str = \"\", end: str = \"\\n\"):\r\n    \"\"\"静默可控的print。\"\"\"\r\n    import src.ptz.core.logger as logger_module\r\n    if not getattr(logger_module.LOG, 'silent', False):\r\n        print(msg, end=end)\r\n\r\nSPEED_PROFILES = {\r\n    'lite': [1, 50, 100],\r\n    'medium': [round(1 + i * (100 - 1) / 7) for i in range(8)],  # 1-100 7等分\r\n    'full': [round(1 + i * (100 - 1) / 25) for i in range(26)],  # 1-100 25等分\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\ndef load_limit_data(model_short: str, mac_clean: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"从limit.json读取限位数据。\r\n\r\n    Args:\r\n        model_short: 短型号\r\n        mac_clean: MAC地址(无冒号,小写)\r\n\r\n    Returns:\r\n        dict: 限位数据\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    import json\r\n    limit_path = get_data_path_read(model_short, mac_clean, 'limit')\r\n    if limit_path is None or not limit_path.exists():\r\n        raise FileNotFoundError(\"limit.json不存在\")\r\n    with open(limit_path, \"r\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\r\n        return json.load(f)\r\n\r\n# Pan轴是360度循环,3600=0\r\n# 所以测试Pan轴时,不要使用3600作为起点,使用0或接近0的值\r\n\r\n\r\ndef measure_speed_single(ptz: Any, axis: str, speed_level: int, raw_csv_path: str,\r\n                         direction: int = 1, zoom_val: int = 10, repeat_idx: int = 0,\r\n                         start_position: float | None = None,\r\n                         limit_data: dict | None = None) -> list[float]:\r\n    \"\"\"测量单轴单速度点的位移。\r\n\r\n    Args:\r\n        ptz: PTZController实例\r\n        axis: 轴名称\r\n        speed_level: 速度等级\r\n        raw_csv_path: CSV路径\r\n        direction: 方向 (1=正向, -1=负向)\r\n        zoom_val: Zoom档位\r\n        repeat_idx: 重复索引\r\n        start_position: 起始位置(绝对移动目标)\r\n        limit_data: 限位数据(从limit.json读取)\r\n        actual_tilt_speed: Tilt轴实际运动速度(正负值,从run_all_tests传入)\r\n\r\n    Returns:\r\n        list[float]: 采样点\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    # 从limit_data读取限位值\r\n    if limit_data is None:\r\n        raise ValueError(\"limit_data不能为空,必须从limit.json读取\")\r\n\r\n    tilt_min = limit_data.get(\"tilt_min\", -200)\r\n    tilt_max = limit_data.get(\"tilt_max\", 900)\r\n    has_flip = limit_data.get(\"has_flip\", False)\r\n    is_infinite = limit_data.get(\"is_infinite\", True)\r\n    pan_min = limit_data.get(\"pan_min\", 0)\r\n    pan_max = limit_data.get(\"pan_max\", 3600)\r\n\r\n    # 所有移动开始前必须判断稳定\r\n    # Pan无限位:从当前位置开始,要求稳定\r\n    # Pan有限位/Tilt:绝对移动到起点,验证稳定\r\n    if start_position is not None:\r\n        # 绝对移动到起点\r\n        ptz.absolute_move(\r\n            pan=int(start_position) if axis == \"pan\" else 1800,\r\n            tilt=int(start_position) if axis == \"tilt\" else 450,\r\n            zoom=zoom_val,\r\n            speed=50\r\n        )\r\n        # 验证稳定:连续20点绝对相等\r\n        stable_count = 0\r\n        for _ in range(300):  # 最多等待30秒\r\n            pos = ptz.get_position()\r\n            actual = pos.get(axis, 0.0)\r\n            if actual == start_position:\r\n                stable_count += 1\r\n                if stable_count >= 20:\r\n                    break\r\n            else:\r\n                stable_count = 0\r\n            time.sleep(0.1)\r\n        if stable_count < 20:\r\n            _print(f\"  警告: 目标{start_position}, 实际{actual:.0f}\")\r\n    else:\r\n        # Pan无限位:从当前位置开始,验证稳定\r\n        stable_count = 0\r\n        last_pos = None\r\n        for _ in range(300):\r\n            pos = ptz.get_position()\r\n            actual = pos.get(axis, 0.0)\r\n            if last_pos is not None and actual == last_pos:\r\n                stable_count += 1\r\n                if stable_count >= 20:\r\n                    break\r\n            else:\r\n                stable_count = 0\r\n            last_pos = actual\r\n            time.sleep(0.1)\r\n        if stable_count < 20:\r\n            _print(f\"  警告: {axis}轴未稳定\")\r\n\r\n    # 连续移动\r\n    # Pan/Tilt轴统一使用 speed_level * direction\r\n    actual_speed = speed_level * direction\r\n\r\n    ptz.continuous_move(\r\n        pan=actual_speed if axis == \"pan\" else 0,\r\n        tilt=actual_speed if axis == \"tilt\" else 0,\r\n    )\r\n\r\n    # 采样(检测限位和翻转)\r\n    samples = []\r\n    hit_limit = False\r\n    flip_detected_sampling = False\r\n\r\n    for _ in range(110):\r\n        position = ptz.get_position()\r\n        pos = position.get(axis, 0.0) if position else 0.0\r\n        samples.append(pos)\r\n        timestamp = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S.%f\")[:-3]\r\n        with open(raw_csv_path, \"a\", newline=\"\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\r\n            writer = csv.writer(f)\r\n            writer.writerow([timestamp, axis, direction, speed_level, zoom_val, repeat_idx, pos])\r\n\r\n        # 检测限位停止\r\n        hit_limit = False\r\n\r\n        if axis == \"pan\":\r\n            # Pan有限位:检测到达限位\r\n            if not is_infinite:\r\n                if pos == pan_max or pos == pan_min:\r\n                    if len(samples) >= 20:\r\n                        recent = samples[-20:]\r\n                        if all(p == pos for p in recent):\r\n                            hit_limit = True\r\n            # Pan无限位:不检测跳变,继续采样到110点\r\n\r\n        elif axis == \"tilt\":\r\n            # Tilt轴限位检测:连续20点达到tmin或tmax\r\n            if pos == tilt_min or pos == tilt_max:\r\n                if len(samples) >= 20:\r\n                    recent = samples[-20:]\r\n                    if all(p == pos for p in recent):\r\n                        hit_limit = True\r\n            \r\n            # Tilt轴翻转检测:达到Tmax后数值降低连续5个点\r\n            if len(samples) >= 5:\r\n                # 检查最近5个点是否都小于前一个点(连续递减)\r\n                if all(samples[i] < samples[i-1] for i in range(-4, 0)):\r\n                    flip_detected_sampling = True\r\n                    break\r\n\r\n        # 到达限位后立即停止\r\n        if hit_limit:\r\n            break\r\n\r\n        time.sleep(0.1)\r\n\r\n    # 停止并验证稳定(连续20点位置不变)\r\n    ptz.stop_move()\r\n    stable_count = 0\r\n    last_pos = None\r\n    for _ in range(300):\r\n        pos = ptz.get_position()\r\n        actual = pos.get(axis, 0.0)\r\n        if last_pos is not None and actual == last_pos:\r\n            stable_count += 1\r\n            if stable_count >= 20:\r\n                break\r\n        else:\r\n            stable_count = 0\r\n        last_pos = actual\r\n        time.sleep(0.1)\r\n\r\n    return samples\r\n\r\n\r\ndef post_process_csv(raw_csv_path: str, mac: str, limit_data: dict | None = None) -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\r\n    \"\"\"数据后处理:计算速度。\r\n\r\n    Args:\r\n        raw_csv_path: CSV文件路径\r\n        mac: MAC地址\r\n        limit_data: 限位数据(包含direction_info)\r\n\r\n    计算规则:\r\n    - 取第6-105个点(索引5:105)\r\n    - 速度 = |end - start| / 10.0\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    results = []\r\n\r\n    with open(raw_csv_path, newline=\"\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\r\n        reader = csv.DictReader(f)\r\n        rows = list(reader)\r\n\r\n    # 按组合分组(包含时间戳)\r\n    groups = {}\r\n    for row in rows:\r\n        axis = row.get(\"axis\", \"\").strip()\r\n        direction = int(row.get(\"direction\", 1))\r\n        speed_level = int(row.get(\"speed_level\", 0))\r\n        zoom = int(row.get(\"zoom\", 0))\r\n        repeat_idx = int(row.get(\"repeat_idx\", 0))\r\n        pos = float(row.get(\"position\", 0.0))\r\n        timestamp = row.get(\"timestamp\", \"\")\r\n        key = (axis, direction, speed_level, zoom)\r\n        groups.setdefault(key, []).append({\"position\": pos, \"repeat_idx\": repeat_idx, \"timestamp\": timestamp})\r\n\r\n    for (axis, direction, speed_level, zoom), entries in groups.items():\r\n        # 读取Pan是否无限位\r\n        is_infinite = limit_data.get(\"is_infinite\", True) if limit_data else True\r\n        \r\n        # 按repeat_idx分组(包含时间戳)\r\n        repeat_groups = {}\r\n        for e in entries:\r\n            idx = e.get(\"repeat_idx\", 0)\r\n            repeat_groups.setdefault(idx, []).append({\"position\": e[\"position\"], \"timestamp\": e[\"timestamp\"]})\r\n\r\n        speeds = []\r\n        movement_direction = \"unknown\"\r\n        hit_limit_flag = False\r\n\r\n        for repeat_idx, entries in repeat_groups.items():\r\n            # 跳变测试可能少于110点,最少需要20点\r\n            if len(entries) < 20:\r\n                continue\r\n\r\n            # 提取位置和时间戳\r\n            positions = [e[\"position\"] for e in entries]\r\n            timestamps = [e[\"timestamp\"] for e in entries]\r\n\r\n            # 判断运动方向(前10个点趋势)\r\n            trend_sum = sum(positions[i] - positions[i-1] for i in range(1, 11))\r\n            movement_dir = \"increasing\" if trend_sum > 0 else (\"decreasing\" if trend_sum < 0 else \"stable\")\r\n            movement_direction = movement_dir\r\n\r\n            # 检测限位/翻转\r\n            valid_end = len(positions)\r\n            flip_detected = False\r\n\r\n            # Pan无限位:不排除跳变,用净位移计算\r\n            # Pan有限位:检测到达限位\r\n            # Tilt轴翻转检测:在限位附近出现的趋势反转\r\n            if axis == \"tilt\":\r\n                for i in range(1, len(positions)):\r\n                    curr = positions[i]\r\n                    prev = positions[i-1]\r\n\r\n                    if movement_dir == \"increasing\":\r\n                        # 递增趋势→经过900→递减趋势(900±200范围内)\r\n                        if curr < prev and curr >= 700:\r\n                            flip_detected = True\r\n                            valid_end = i\r\n                            break\r\n\r\n                    elif movement_dir == \"decreasing\":\r\n                        # 递减趋势→经过-200→递增趋势(-200±200范围内)\r\n                        if curr > prev and curr <= 0:\r\n                            flip_detected = True\r\n                            valid_end = i\r\n                            break\r\n\r\n            # 选择有效数据\r\n            valid_start = 5  # 排除启停5个点\r\n\r\n            if flip_detected:\r\n                # 翻转:取到翻转前,不排除最后5点\r\n                valid_positions = positions[valid_start:valid_end]\r\n                valid_timestamps = timestamps[valid_start:valid_end]\r\n            else:\r\n                # 无翻转:取中间10秒(100个点)\r\n                valid_positions = positions[valid_start:valid_start + 100]\r\n                valid_timestamps = timestamps[valid_start:valid_start + 100]\r\n\r\n            if len(valid_positions) < 2:\r\n                continue\r\n\r\n            # Pan无限位:检测跳变次数,分段计算距离\r\n            # 其他情况:累加位移\r\n            if axis == \"pan\" and is_infinite:\r\n                # 检测跳变点(相邻两点差值>1800)\r\n                jump_points = []\r\n                for i in range(1, len(valid_positions)):\r\n                    diff = valid_positions[i] - valid_positions[i-1]\r\n                    if abs(diff) > 1800:\r\n                        jump_points.append(i)\r\n                \r\n                # 分段计算距离(绝对值)\r\n                total_move = 0.0\r\n                prev_pos = valid_positions[0]\r\n                \r\n                for jump_idx in jump_points:\r\n                    # 跳变前的一段:从prev_pos到边界\r\n                    total_move += abs(prev_pos - 0)\r\n                    # 更新prev_pos为跳变后的位置\r\n                    prev_pos = valid_positions[jump_idx]\r\n                \r\n                # 最后一段\r\n                if len(jump_points) == 0:\r\n                    # 无跳变:直接计算起点到终点\r\n                    total_move = abs(prev_pos - valid_positions[-1])\r\n                else:\r\n                    # 有跳变:从边界到终点\r\n                    total_move += abs(3600 - valid_positions[-1])\r\n            else:\r\n                # 累加位移\r\n                total_move = 0.0\r\n                for i in range(1, len(valid_positions)):\r\n                    diff = valid_positions[i] - valid_positions[i-1]\r\n                    total_move += diff\r\n\r\n            # 用时间戳计算实际时间\r\n            from datetime import datetime\r\n            start_ts = datetime.strptime(valid_timestamps[0], '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S.%f')\r\n            end_ts = datetime.strptime(valid_timestamps[-1], '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S.%f')\r\n            valid_time = (end_ts - start_ts).total_seconds()\r\n\r\n            speed = abs(total_move) / valid_time if valid_time > 0 else 0.0\r\n            speeds.append(speed)\r\n\r\n        avg_speed = sum(speeds) / len(speeds) if speeds else 0.0\r\n\r\n        # 判断同/反向\r\n        # 从limit_data读取方向信息\r\n\n⚠️ [... middle content omitted — showing head and tail ...]\n\n                                start_pos = tilt_min  # 往大走\r\n                            else:\r\n                                start_pos = tilt_max  # 往小走\r\n\r\n                        # 测速(不再每次回HOME)\r\n                        measure_speed_single(\r\n                            ptz, axis, speed, str(csv_path),\r\n                            direction, zoom_val, repeat_idx, start_pos, limit_data\r\n                        )\r\n\r\n    _print()\r\n\r\n    # 后处理\r\n    all_results = post_process_csv(str(csv_path), mac_clean, limit_data)\r\n\r\n    # 测试完成后回到HOME\r\n    ptz.goto_preset(10)\r\n    ptz.wait_stable()\r\n    _print(\"\\nSpeed测试完成,设备已回到HOME位\")\r\n\r\n    # 保存到speed.json\r\n    try:\r\n        import json\r\n        output_file = get_data_path_write(model_short, mac_clean, 'speed')\r\n        with open(output_file, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\r\n            json.dump({\r\n                \"success\": len(all_results) > 0,\r\n                \"total_tests\": len(all_results),\r\n                \"speed_profile\": speed_profile,\r\n                \"results\": all_results,\r\n                \"csv_path\": str(csv_path)\r\n            }, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\r\n    except Exception:\r\n        pass\r\n\r\n    return all_results\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nclass SpeedTester:\r\n    def __init__(self, ptz: Any) -> None:\r\n        self.ptz = ptz\r\n\r\n    def run_all_tests(self, config: Any = None, speed_profile: str = 'lite') -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\r\n        return run_all_tests(self.ptz, config, speed_profile)\r\n\r\n\r\n# ================================================================ #\r\n#  独立运行入口\r\n# ================================================================ #\r\n\r\ndef run_speed_test(ip: str = None, username: str = \"admin\", password: str = \"\", port: int = 80, speed_profile: str = 'lite') -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"独立运行Speed测试。\r\n    \r\n    自动读取活跃设备，无需指定IP。\r\n    \r\n    Args:\r\n        ip: 设备IP（可选，默认从活跃设备读取）\r\n        username: 用户名\r\n        password: 密码\r\n        port: 端口\r\n        speed_profile: 速度档位模式\r\n    \r\n    Returns:\r\n        测试结果\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    from src.ptz.isapi.client import ISAPIClient\r\n    from src.ptz.isapi.ptz import PTZController\r\n    \r\n    # 读取活跃设备\r\n    if ip is None:\r\n        device = get_current_device()\r\n        if device is None:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"error\": \"未设置活跃设备，请先用 device.py add 添加设备\"}\r\n        ip = device.get(\"ip\", \"\")\r\n        port = device.get(\"port\", 80)\r\n        if not ip:\r\n            return {\"success\": False, \"error\": \"活跃设备未配置IP\"}\r\n    \r\n    # 连接设备\r\n    client = ISAPIClient(ip=ip, username=username, password=password, port=port)\r\n    if not client.verify_credentials():\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"error\": f\"设备认证失败: {ip}\"}\r\n    \r\n    ptz = PTZController(client)\r\n    \r\n    # 运行测试\r\n    results = run_all_tests(ptz, None, speed_profile)\r\n    \r\n    # 更新设备信息\r\n    device_info = get_current_device()\r\n    if device_info and device_info.get(\"mac\"):\r\n        update_device_info(device_info[\"mac\"], last_speed_test=len(results))\r\n    \r\n    return {\r\n        \"success\": len(results) > 0,\r\n        \"total_tests\": len(results),\r\n        \"results\": results\r\n    }\r\n\r\n\r\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\r\n    import argparse\r\n    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"AstroHub Speed测试\")\r\n    parser.add_argument(\"--ip\", type=str, help=\"设备IP (默认从配置读取)\")\r\n    parser.add_argument(\"--username\", type=str, default=\"admin\", help=\"用户名\")\r\n    parser.add_argument(\"--password\", type=str, default=\"\", help=\"密码\")\r\n    parser.add_argument(\"--port\", type=int, default=80, help=\"端口\")\r\n    parser.add_argument(\"--profile\", type=str, default=\"lite\", choices=['lite', 'medium', 'full'], help=\"速度档位模式\")\r\n    args = parser.parse_args()\r\n    \r\n    _print(\"=\" * 50)\r\n    _print(\"AstroHub Speed测试\")\r\n    _print(\"=\" * 50)\r\n    \r\n    result = run_speed_test(ip=args.ip, username=args.username, password=args.password, port=args.port, speed_profile=args.profile)\r\n    \r\n    if result.get(\"success\"):\r\n        _print(f\"[完成] 速度测试: {result.get('total_tests', 0)} 项\")\r\n    else:\r\n        _print(f\"[失败] {result.get('error', '未知错误')}\")[... 5907 more characters truncated]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780132683589}}
{"type":"message","id":"d174ec4a","parentId":"f75cbc23","timestamp":"2026-05-30T09:18:11.594Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"..."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-fe6a9820a7f345ae998a9f022dc2b703","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\device_path.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-00e0f53aac5948a281c2451d94ca06a2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\device_config.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":25293,"output":67,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25360,"cost":{"input":0.025293,"output":0.0002144,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0255074}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780132683590,"responseId":"cht000d3a2d@dx19e782d2959b992462"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6c2d12d6","parentId":"d174ec4a","timestamp":"2026-05-30T09:18:11.643Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-fe6a9820a7f345ae998a9f022dc2b703","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nAstroHub v2.0 - 设备数据路径管理\n\n统一管理设备数据存储路径：\n- 设备标识：MAC地址（从ISAPI获取）\n- 路径规范：data/{短型号}_{mac}/{YYYYMMDD}_{序号}/\n- 读取规则：永远读最新记录\n\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport re\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\n\ndef get_device_info(ptz: Any) -> dict[str, str]:\n    \"\"\"从设备获取唯一标识信息。\n\n    Args:\n        ptz: PTZController实例\n\n    Returns:\n        dict: {mac, model, model_short, serial}\n    \"\"\"\n    # 从PTZController获取ISAPIClient\n    client = ptz.client if hasattr(ptz, 'client') else ptz\n\n    # 获取设备信息\n    resp = client.get('/System/deviceInfo')\n    xml = resp.xml\n\n    # 解析XML\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\n    root = ET.fromstring(xml)\n\n    # 提取字段\n    mac = \"\"\n    model = \"\"\n    serial = \"\"\n\n    for child in root:\n        tag = child.tag.split('}')[-1] if '}' in child.tag else child.tag\n        if tag == 'macAddress':\n            mac = child.text or \"\"\n        elif tag == 'model':\n            model = child.text or \"\"\n        elif tag == 'serialNumber':\n            serial = child.text or \"\"\n\n    # MAC地址去除冒号，转小写\n    mac_clean = mac.replace(':', '').lower()\n\n    # 短型号：取前缀（去掉后缀数字和字母）\n    # iDS-2DF8C832IXS-A -> iDS-2DF8C\n    model_short = model\n    if len(model) > 8:\n        model_short = model[:8]\n        while model_short and model_short[-1].isdigit():\n            model_short = model_short[:-1]\n\n    return {\n        'mac': mac,\n        'mac_clean': mac_clean,\n        'model': model,\n        'model_short': model_short,\n        'serial': serial\n    }\n\n\ndef get_device_dir(model_short: str, mac_clean: str) -> Path:\n    \"\"\"获取设备根目录路径。\n\n    Args:\n        model_short: 短型号\n        mac_clean: MAC地址（无冒号，小写）\n\n    Returns:\n        Path: data/{model_short}_{mac_clean}/\n    \"\"\"\n    return Path('data') / f'{model_short}_{mac_clean}'\n\n\ndef find_latest_session(model_short: str, mac_clean: str) -> Path | None:\n    \"\"\"查找最新的测试目录。\n\n    Args:\n        model_short: 短型号\n        mac_clean: MAC地址（无冒号，小写）\n\n    Returns:\n        Path: 最新目录路径，如不存在返回None\n    \"\"\"\n    device_dir = get_device_dir(model_short, mac_clean)\n    if not device_dir.exists():\n        return None\n\n    # 列出所有 {YYYYMMDD}_{序号} 目录\n    pattern = re.compile(r'^(\\d{8})_(\\d{3})$')\n    sessions = []\n    for d in device_dir.iterdir():\n        if d.is_dir():\n            match = pattern.match(d.name)\n            if match:\n                date_str = match.group(1)\n                seq = int(match.group(2))\n                sessions.append((date_str, seq, d))\n\n    if not sessions:\n        return None\n\n    # 按日期和序号排序，返回最新的\n    sessions.sort(key=lambda x: (x[0], x[2]))\n    return sessions[-1][2]\n\n\ndef create_new_session(model_short: str, mac_clean: str) -> Path:\n    \"\"\"创建新的测试目录。\n\n    Args:\n        model_short: 短型号\n        mac_clean: MAC地址（无冒号，小写）\n\n    Returns:\n        Path: 新目录路径\n    \"\"\"\n    device_dir = get_device_dir(model_short, mac_clean)\n    device_dir.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n\n    today = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\n\n    # 查找当天已有的目录\n    pattern = re.compile(rf'^{today}_(\\d{3})$')\n    max_seq = 0\n    for d in device_dir.iterdir():\n        if d.is_dir():\n            match = pattern.match(d.name)\n            if match:\n                seq = int(match.group(1))\n                max_seq = max(max_seq, seq)\n\n    # 新序号\n    new_seq = max_seq + 1\n    new_dir = device_dir / f'{today}_{new_seq:03d}'\n    new_dir.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    return new_dir\n\n\ndef get_data_path_read(model_short: str, mac_clean: str, test_type: str) -> Path | None:\n    \"\"\"获取读取路径（设备目录下最新的对应文件）。\n\n    Args:\n        model_short: 短型号\n        mac_clean: MAC地址（无冒号，小写）\n        test_type: 测试类型 (function/limit/speed)\n\n    Returns:\n        Path: 文件路径，如不存在返回None\n    \"\"\"\n    device_dir = get_device_dir(model_short, mac_clean)\n    if not device_dir.exists():\n        return None\n\n    # 查找所有包含目标文件的目录，返回最新的\n    pattern = re.compile(r'^(\\d{8})_(\\d{3})$')\n    latest_file = None\n    latest_time = None\n\n    for d in device_dir.iterdir():\n        if d.is_dir():\n            target_file = d / f'{test_type}.json'\n            if target_file.exists():\n                file_time = target_file.stat().st_mtime\n                if latest_time is None or file_time > latest_time:\n                    latest_time = file_time\n                    latest_file = target_file\n\n    return latest_file\n\n\ndef get_data_path_write(model_short: str, mac_clean: str, test_type: str) -> Path:\n    \"\"\"获取写入路径（每次创建新序号目录）。\n\n    Args:\n        model_short: 短型号\n        mac_clean: MAC地址（无冒号，小写）\n        test_type: 测试类型 (function/limit/speed)\n\n    Returns:\n        Path: 文件路径\n    \"\"\"\n    device_dir = get_device_dir(model_short, mac_clean)\n    device_dir.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n\n    today = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\n\n    # 查找当天已有的最大序号\n    pattern = re.compile(rf'^{today}_(\\d{{3}})$')\n    max_seq = 0\n    for d in device_dir.iterdir():\n        if d.is_dir():\n            match = pattern.match(d.name)\n            if match:\n                seq = int(match.group(1))\n                max_seq = max(max_seq, seq)\n\n    # 每次都创建新序号\n    new_seq = max_seq + 1\n    session_dir = device_dir / f'{today}_{new_seq:03d}'\n    session_dir.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    return session_dir / f'{test_type}.json'"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780132691643}}
{"type":"message","id":"179a9055","parentId":"6c2d12d6","timestamp":"2026-05-30T09:18:11.643Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-00e0f53aac5948a281c2451d94ca06a2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nAstroHub v2.0 - 设备配置管理\n\n统一管理设备配置：\n- 读取/写入 device_config.json\n- 当前设备、历史设备\n- IP/MAC/型号等信息\n\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nCONFIG_FILE = Path(__file__).parent.parent.parent / \"data\" / \"device_config.json\"\n\n\ndef ensure_config() -> Path:\n    \"\"\"确保配置文件存在。\"\"\"\n    CONFIG_FILE.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    if not CONFIG_FILE.exists():\n        save_config({\n            \"current_device\": None,\n            \"devices\": {}\n        })\n    return CONFIG_FILE\n\n\ndef load_config() -> dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"加载设备配置。\"\"\"\n    ensure_config()\n    with open(CONFIG_FILE, \"r\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n        return json.load(f)\n\n\ndef save_config(config: dict[str, Any]) -> None:\n    \"\"\"保存设备配置。\"\"\"\n    CONFIG_FILE.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    with open(CONFIG_FILE, \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n        json.dump(config, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n\n\ndef get_current_device() -> dict[str, Any] | None:\n    \"\"\"获取当前设备信息。\"\"\"\n    config = load_config()\n    current_mac = config.get(\"current_device\")\n    if not current_mac:\n        return None\n    return config.get(\"devices\", {}).get(current_mac)\n\n\ndef set_current_device(mac: str, ip: str = \"\", model: str = \"\", port: int = 80) -> None:\n    \"\"\"设置当前设备。\"\"\"\n    config = load_config()\n    mac_clean = mac.replace(\":\", \"\").lower()\n    \n    config[\"current_device\"] = mac_clean\n    if mac_clean not in config.get(\"devices\", {}):\n        config.setdefault(\"devices\", {})[mac_clean] = {}\n    \n    config[\"devices\"][mac_clean][\"mac\"] = mac_clean\n    if ip:\n        config[\"devices\"][mac_clean][\"ip\"] = ip\n    if model:\n        config[\"devices\"][mac_clean][\"model\"] = model\n    config[\"devices\"][mac_clean][\"port\"] = port\n    \n    save_config(config)\n\n\ndef update_device_info(mac: str, **kwargs) -> None:\n    \"\"\"更新设备信息。\"\"\"\n    config = load_config()\n    mac_clean = mac.replace(\":\", \"\").lower()\n    \n    if mac_clean not in config.get(\"devices\", {}):\n        config.setdefault(\"devices\", {})[mac_clean] = {\"mac\": mac_clean}\n    \n    config[\"devices\"][mac_clean].update(kwargs)\n    save_config(config)\n\n\ndef list_devices() -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\n    \"\"\"列出所有历史设备。\"\"\"\n    config = load_config()\n    return list(config.get(\"devices\", {}).values())\n\n\ndef get_device_by_mac(mac: str) -> dict[str, Any] | None:\n    \"\"\"根据MAC获取设备信息。\"\"\"\n    config = load_config()\n    mac_clean = mac.replace(\":\", \"\").lower()\n    return config.get(\"devices\", {}).get(mac_clean)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780132691643}}
