{"type":"message","id":"a881b69d","parentId":"a0c22337","timestamp":"2026-05-30T09:18:47.444Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d693835bb4d84f1da15ff322","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"编号,问题,当前逻辑,正确逻辑,状态,修复日期\n1,测试顺序错误,同方向走3次 → 换方向走3次,正向反向交替重复3次,已修复,2026-05-29\n2,速度计算时间写死,len(valid) * 0.1,用时间戳计算实际时间,已修复,2026-05-29\n3,测试结束后未验证稳定,stop_move() + sleep(2),stop_move() + 验证20点稳定,已修复,2026-05-29\n4,后处理未使用时间戳,只读 position,读 timestamp + position,已修复,2026-05-29\n5,Tilt轴翻转检测逻辑,检测900±200范围内递减,递增趋势→经过900→递减趋势检测趋势变化,已修复,2026-05-29\n6,Pan轴有限位时起止位置,已有逻辑,根据 positive_command_increases 确定起点,已实现,\n7,Pan轴3600跳变计算,diff > 1800 或 diff < -1800,前后两个数值相差超过1800判定为跳变,已实现,\n8,硬编码 actual_tilt_speed,已删除,统一使用 speed_level * direction,已修复,2026-05-29\n9,起点判断未读 direction_info,已修复,从 limit.json 读取 positive_command_increases,已修复,2026-05-29\n10,Pan轴无限位起点规则,从当前位置开始,正向完成后原地反向不移动到任何点,已实现,\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780132727444}}
{"type":"message","id":"995a3de4","parentId":"a881b69d","timestamp":"2026-05-30T09:19:10.974Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"分析代码后，发现几个问题：\n\n**问题1: Pan无限位距离计算算法错误**\n当前代码在检测跳变后计算距离的方法不对。根据文档：\n- 跳变前：从起点到边界(0)，距离 = abs(起点 - 0)\n- 跳变后：从边界(3600)到终点，距离 = abs(3600 - 终点)\n\n但当前代码使用 `prev_pos` 作为分段起点，逻辑混乱。\n\n**问题2: Tilt翻转检测位置错误**\n当前代码检测 `curr >= 700` 才认为翻转，但应该是检测趋势变化而非固定位置。\n\n**问题3: 写入路径逻辑检查**\n`get_data_path_write` 每次创建新目录，正确。\n\n修复算法问题："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-436c3575f27e46fd86d71b38075021d6","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"            # Pan无限位:检测跳变次数,分段计算距离\n            # 其他情况:累加位移\n            if axis == \"pan\" and is_infinite:\n                # 检测跳变点(相邻两点差值绝对值>1800)\n                jump_indices = []\n                for i in range(1, len(valid_positions)):\n                    diff = valid_positions[i] - valid_positions[i-1]\n                    if abs(diff) > 1800:\n                        jump_indices.append(i)\n                \n                # 分段计算距离(绝对值累加)\n                total_move = 0.0\n                start_pos = valid_positions[0]\n                \n                if len(jump_indices) == 0:\n                    # 无跳变:直接计算起点到终点\n                    total_move = abs(valid_positions[-1] - start_pos)\n                else:\n                    # 有跳变:分段计算\n                    prev_idx = 0\n                    for jump_idx in jump_indices:\n                        # 跳变前:从上一段起点到边界(0或3600)\n                        prev_pos = valid_positions[prev_idx]\n                        curr_pos = valid_positions[jump_idx]\n                        \n                        # 判断跳变方向\n                        if curr_pos < prev_pos:\n                            # 正向跳变:从3600跳到0附近\n                            # 跳变前:从prev_pos到3600\n                            total_move += abs(3600 - prev_pos)\n                        else:\n                            # 反向跳变:从0跳到3600附近\n                            # 跳变前:从prev_pos到0\n                            total_move += abs(prev_pos - 0)\n                        \n                        prev_idx = jump_idx\n                    \n                    # 最后一段:从跳变点到终点\n                    last_jump_pos = valid_positions[jump_indices[-1]]\n                    if last_jump_pos < start_pos:\n                        # 正向跳变后:从0到终点\n                        total_move += abs(valid_positions[-1] - 0)\n                    else:\n                        # 反向跳变后:从3600到终点\n                        total_move += abs(3600 - valid_positions[-1])","oldText":"            # Pan无限位:检测跳变次数,分段计算距离\n            # 其他情况:累加位移\n            if axis == \"pan\" and is_infinite:\n                # 检测跳变点(相邻两点差值>1800)\n                jump_points = []\n                for i in range(1, len(valid_positions)):\n                    diff = valid_positions[i] - valid_positions[i-1]\n                    if abs(diff) > 1800:\n                        jump_points.append(i)\n                \n                # 分段计算距离(绝对值)\n                total_move = 0.0\n                prev_pos = valid_positions[0]\n                \n                for jump_idx in jump_points:\n                    # 跳变前的一段:从prev_pos到边界\n                    total_move += abs(prev_pos - 0)\n                    # 更新prev_pos为跳变后的位置\n                    prev_pos = valid_positions[jump_idx]\n                \n                # 最后一段\n                if len(jump_points) == 0:\n                    # 无跳变:直接计算起点到终点\n                    total_move = abs(prev_pos - valid_positions[-1])\n                else:\n                    # 有跳变:从边界到终点\n                    total_move += abs(3600 - valid_positions[-1])"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\speed.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":29517,"output":975,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30492,"cost":{"input":0.029516999999999998,"output":0.0031200000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.032637}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780132727445,"responseId":"cht000db0e7@dx19e782dd11bb958402"}}
