{"type":"message","id":"aeded3f7","parentId":"d0d8030e","timestamp":"2026-05-30T09:45:14.730Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**问题确认：`set_current_device` 函数不保存 `username` 和 `password`。**\n\n需要修复：\n1. `set_current_device` 函数添加 `username` 和 `password` 参数\n2. `device.py` 的 `add_device` 函数传递这两个参数"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-ca61f78681f440dba34e5fac81b56ba7","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"def set_current_device(mac: str, ip: str = \"\", model: str = \"\", port: int = 80, username: str = \"\", password: str = \"\") -> None:\n    \"\"\"设置当前设备。\"\"\"\n    config = load_config()\n    mac_clean = mac.replace(\"\", \"\").lower()\n    \n    config[\"current_device\"] = mac_clean\n    if mac_clean not in config.get(\"devices\", {}):\n        config.setdefault(\"devices\", {})[mac_clean] = {}\n    \n    config[\"devices\"][mac_clean][\"mac\"] = mac_clean\n    if ip:\n        config[\"devices\"][mac_clean][\"ip\"] = ip\n    if model:\n        config[\"devices\"][mac_clean][\"model\"] = model\n    config[\"devices\"][mac_clean][\"port\"] = port\n    if username:\n        config[\"devices\"][mac_clean][\"username\"] = username\n    if password:\n        config[\"devices\"][mac_clean][\"password\"] = password","oldText":"def set_current_device(mac: str, ip: str = \"\", model: str = \"\", port: int = 80) -> None:\n    \"\"\"设置当前设备。\"\"\"\n    config = load_config()\n    mac_clean = mac.replace(\"\", \"\").lower()\n    \n    config[\"current_device\"] = mac_clean\n    if mac_clean not in config.get(\"devices\", {}):\n        config.setdefault(\"devices\", {})[mac_clean] = {}\n    \n    config[\"devices\"][mac_clean][\"mac\"] = mac_clean\n    if ip:\n        config[\"devices\"][mac_clean][\"ip\"] = ip\n    if model:\n        config[\"devices\"][mac_clean][\"model\"] = model\n    config[\"devices\"][mac_clean][\"port\"] = port"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\device_config.py"}}],"a