{"type":"message","id":"a8bdc8a5","parentId":"2d5ce5c4","timestamp":"2026-05-30T09:47:22.778Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**documents 目录文件：**\n\n| 文件 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `data_storage_spec.md` | 数据存储规范 |\n| `function_test.md` | 功能测试文档 |\n| `limit_test.md` | 限位测试文档 |\n| `speed_test.md` | 速度测试文档 |\n\n检查哪个脚本是初始运行、需要写入设备信息："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6c811533da654cf28d5ce0cc","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\documents\\data_storage_spec.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":57511,"output":109,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57620,"cost":{"input":0.057511,"output":0.0003488,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0578598}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780134436143,"responseId":"cht000f0770@dx19e7847e377b8ab592"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f4befb40","parentId":"a8bdc8a5","timestamp":"2026-05-30T09:47:22.819Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6c811533da654cf28d5ce0cc","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# AstroHub 数据存储规范\n\n## 1. 设备唯一标识\n\n设备唯一标识使用 **MAC地址**，从ISAPI接口获取：\n\n```\nGET /System/deviceInfo\n→ <macAddress>24:0f:9b:76:41:93</macAddress>\n```\n\nMAC地址处理：\n- 去除冒号\n- 转小写\n- 示例：`240f9b764193`\n\n## 2. 文件路径规范\n\n### 2.1 目录结构\n\n```\nastrohub/\n├── data/\n│   └── {短型号}_{mac_clean}/\n│       └── {YYYYMMDD}_{序号}/\n│           ├── function.json\n│           ├── limit.json\n│           └── speed.json\n└── documents/\n    └── DATA_STORAGE_SPEC.md\n```\n\n### 2.2 路径组成\n\n| 组成部分 | 说明 | 示例 |\n|---------|------|------|\n| 短型号 | 设备型号前缀，取前8字符去除末尾数字 | `iDS-2DF8C` |\n| MAC地址 | 无冒号小写 | `240f9b764193` |\n| 日期序号 | YYYYMMDD_序号 | `20260528_001` |\n\n### 2.3 完整路径示例\n\n```\ndata/iDS-2DF8C_240f9b764193/20260528_001/function.json\ndata/iDS-2DF8C_240f9b764193/20260528_001/limit.json\n```\n\n## 3. 文件命名规范\n\n| 测试类型 | JSON文件 |\n|---------|---------|\n| 功能测试 | function.json |\n| 限位测试 | limit.json |\n| 速度测试 | speed.json |\n\n## 4. 读取规则\n\n**匹配设备 → 找最新目录**：\n\n1. 根据 MAC 和型号匹配设备目录\n2. 列出所有 `{YYYYMMDD}_{序号}` 子目录\n3. 按日期和序号排序\n4. 选择最新的目录\n\n## 5. 写入规则\n\n1. 查找设备目录是否存在\n2. 如存在，找最新序号目录\n3. 如当天已有记录，序号+1\n4. 如当天无记录，序号=001\n5. 如设备目录不存在，创建 `YYYYMMDD_001`\n\n## 6. 禁止事项\n\n- ❌ 禁止硬编码路径\n- ❌ 禁止使用临时命名（如 `test_all`、`default`）\n- ❌ 禁止在模块内直接拼接路径字符串\n\n## 7. 正确做法\n\n- ✅ 使用相对路径（相对于astrohub根目录）\n- ✅ 使用 `device_path.py` 模块统一管理路径\n- ✅ 从设备实时获取MAC地址作为唯一标识\n- ✅ 永远读取最新记录\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780134442819}}
{"type":"message","id":"8caad11c","parentId":"f4befb40","timestamp":"2026-05-30T09:47:28.313Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"检查 function_test.md（初始运行）："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-c0ed8be147724080998a210adeed2f6a","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\documents\\function_test.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":53281,"output":39,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53320,"cost":{"input":0.053280999999999995,"output":0.0001248,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.053405799999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780134442820,"responseId":"cht000f09e5@dx19e7847fb3eb8ab592"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1551a6ff","parentId":"8caad11c","timestamp":"2026-05-30T09:47:28.362Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-c0ed8be147724080998a210adeed2f6a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Function 测试开发文档\n\n## 概述\n\nFunction测试用于探测PTZ设备的各项功能支持情况，包括18项设备功能（P4.1-P4.21）。\n\n---\n\n## 核心流程\n\n```\n1. 连接设备 → 2. 验证HOME预置点 → 3. 探测功能 → 4. 保存结果\n```\n\n---\n\n## 步骤详解\n\n### 步骤1：设备连接\n\n```python\nfrom src.ptz.isapi.client import ISAPIClient\nfrom src.ptz.isapi.ptz import PTZController\n\nclient = ISAPIClient(ip, username, password, port)\nptz = PTZController(client)\n```\n\n**易错点**：\n- 端口号默认80，不是443\n- 认证失败时检查用户名密码是否正确\n\n---\n\n### 步骤2：验证HOME预置点\n\n**目的**：确保预置点10存在且坐标正确（pan=1800, tilt=450, zoom=10）\n\n```python\ndef verify_home_preset(client):\n    ptz = PTZController(client)\n    \n    # 尝试调用预置点10\n    ptz.goto_preset(10)\n    time.sleep(2)\n    pos = ptz.get_position()\n    \n    # 验证坐标\n    expected = {\"pan\": 1800, \"tilt\": 450, \"zoom\": 10}\n    pan_ok = abs(pos.get(\"pan\", 0) - expected[\"pan\"]) <= 10\n    tilt_ok = abs(pos.get(\"tilt\", 0) - expected[\"tilt\"]) <= 5\n    zoom_ok = abs(pos.get(\"zoom\", 0) - expected[\"zoom\"]) <= 1\n    \n    if pan_ok and tilt_ok and zoom_ok:\n        return {\"success\": True, \"preset_exists\": True}\n    \n    # 坐标不匹配，需要设置\n    ptz.set_preset(10)\n    return {\"success\": True, \"preset_exists\": False}\n```\n\n**易错点**：\n- 预置点可能不存在或坐标错误\n- 需要等待设备稳定后再读取位置\n\n---\n\n### 步骤3：探测功能\n\n每项功能探测流程：\n\n```\n1. GET端点探测 → 2. 读取当前值 → 3. 读取取值范围 → 4. 修改测试 → 5. 恢复原始值\n```\n\n#### 3.1 GET端点探测\n\n```python\nendpoint = f\"/Image/channels/{channel}/IrLight\"\nresp = client.get(endpoint)\nif resp.status_code == 200:\n    # 端点支持\n```\n\n#### 3.2 读取当前值\n\n```python\nimport xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\nroot = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\nfor elem in root.iter():\n    tag = elem.tag.split('}')[-1] if '}' in elem.tag else elem.tag\n    if tag.lower() == \"brightnesslimit\":\n        current_value = elem.text\n```\n\n#### 3.3 读取取值范围\n\n从XML的`<min>`和`<max>`属性读取：\n```python\nfor elem in root.iter():\n    if elem.get(\"min\") and elem.get(\"max\"):\n        min_val = int(elem.get(\"min\"))\n        max_val = int(elem.get(\"max\"))\n```\n\n**易错点**：\n- XML可能没有min/max属性，需要使用CSV文档中的默认值\n- 忽略XML命名空间\n\n#### 3.4 修改测试\n\n```python\n# 构造测试XML\ntest_xml = f'''<IrLight version=\"2.0\">\n    <brightnessLimit>{test_value}</brightnessLimit>\n</IrLight>'''\n\n# PUT修改\nresp = client.put(endpoint, test_xml)\n\n# GET验证\nresp = client.get(endpoint)\n# 检查值是否变化\n```\n\n#### 3.5 恢复原始值\n\n```python\nrestore_xml = f'''<IrLight version=\"2.0\">\n    <brightnessLimit>{original_value}</brightnessLimit>\n</IrLight>'''\nclient.put(endpoint, restore_xml)\n```\n\n---\n\n### 步骤4：保存结果\n\n```python\nfrom src.advanced.device_path import get_device_info, get_data_path_write\n\n# 获取设备信息\ndevice_info = get_device_info(ptz)\nmodel_short = device_info['model_short']\nmac_clean = device_info['mac_clean']\n\n# 保存到JSON\noutput_file = get_data_path_write(model_short, mac_clean, 'function')\nwith open(output_file, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    json.dump(result, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n```\n\n**路径规范**：`data/{短型号}_{MAC}/{YYYYMMDD}_{序号}/function.json`\n\n---\n\n## 易错点汇总\n\n### 1. HOME预置点设置\n\n**错误**：直接调用`set_preset(10)`，不传入坐标\n**正确**：\n```python\n# 先移动到HOME坐标\nptz.absolute_move(pan=1800, tilt=450, zoom=10, speed=50)\n# 再设置预置点\nptz.set_preset(10, pan=1800, tilt=450, zoom=10, name='HOME')\n```\n\n### 2. Iris光圈控制\n\n**错误**：使用相对值调整\n**正确**：Iris是离散值，只能从固定列表选择\n```python\nIRIS_LEVELS = [160, 200, 240, 280, 340, 400, 480, 560, 680, 960, 1100, 1400, 1600, 1900, 2200]\n```\n\n### 3. XML命名空间\n\n**错误**：直接查找`brightnessLimit`\n**正确**：去除命名空间后再匹配\n```python\ntag = elem.tag.split('}')[-1] if '}' in elem.tag else elem.tag\n```\n\n### 4. 稳定检测\n\n**错误**：使用偏差容忍 `abs(t - last) < 0.5`\n**正确**：精确相等 `t == last`\n```python\nstable_count = 0\nfor _ in range(300):\n    pos = ptz.get_position()\n    if pos.get(\"pan\") == 1800:\n        stable_count += 1\n        if stable_count >= 20:\n            break\n    else:\n        stable_count = 0\n    time.sleep(0.1)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 依赖关系\n\nFunction测试是第一个测试，无前置依赖。\n\n后续测试依赖：\n- Limit测试需要`function.json`存在\n- Speed测试需要`limit.json`存在\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780134448362}}
