{"type":"message","id":"08df904c","parentId":"e649b59f","timestamp":"2026-05-30T12:23:53.075Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"记录错误到 `.learnings/ERRORS.md`："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-e78056dbd135475e98c1bfa18deeff63","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\.learnings\\ERRORS.md","content":"# 错误记录\n\n## ERR-20260530-001: 硬编码账号密码\n\n**时间**: 2026-05-30 17:18\n**优先级**: HIGH\n**状态**: 已修复\n**摘要**: speed.py、function.py、limit.py 使用硬编码默认值 username=\"admin\", password=\"\"\n\n**错误代码**:\n```python\ndef run_speed_test(username: str = \"admin\", password: str = \"\", port: int = 80):\n```\n\n**修复**:\n```python\ndef run_speed_test(username: str = None, password: str = None, port: int = None):\n    # 从配置文件读取\n    device_config = load_device_config('240f9b764193')\n    if username is None:\n        username = device_config.username or \"admin\"\n    if password is None:\n        password = device_config.password or \"\"\n```\n\n**教训**:\n- 禁止硬编码账号密码\n- 必须从配置文件读取\n- 配置文件路径: `data/devices/{MAC}.json`\n\n---\n\n## ERR-20260530-002: 过度开发 device.py\n\n**时间**: 2026-05-30 17:46\n**优先级**: HIGH\n**状态**: 已删除\n**摘要**: 未经老板要求创建 device.py 脚本\n\n**错误**:\n- 创建了 device.py（设备管理脚本）\n- 不是老板要求的\n- 过度开发\n\n**修复**:\n- 删除 device.py\n- 使用 onboarding.py 作为初始化脚本\n\n**教训**:\n- 禁止未经要求创建新脚本\n- 初始化脚本路径: `src/advanced/onboarding.py`\n- 配置文件写入: `src/advanced/config_writer.py`\n\n---\n\n## ERR-20260530-003: DeviceConfig 缺少账号密码字段\n\n**时间**: 2026-05-30 17:51\n**优先级**: HIGH\n**状态**: 已修复\n**摘要**: config_writer.py 的 DeviceConfig 数据结构缺少 username/password 字段\n\n**错误代码**:\n```python\n@dataclass\nclass DeviceConfig:\n    mac: str = \"\"\n    ip: str = \"\"\n    model: str = \"\"\n    # 缺少 username, password\n```\n\n**修复**:\n```python\n@dataclass\nclass DeviceConfig:\n    mac: str = \"\"\n    ip: str = \"\"\n    port: int = 80\n    username: str = \"admin\"\n    password: str = \"\"\n```\n\n**教训**:\n- 设备配置必须包含账号密码\n- 配置文件路径: `data/devices/{MAC}.json`\n\n---\n\n## ERR-20260530-004: Pan轴多次跳变距离计算错误\n\n**时间**: 2026-05-30 17:36\n**优先级**: MEDIUM\n**状态**: 已修复\n**摘要**: Pan无限位多次跳变时距离计算只处理最后一段，中间段丢失\n\n**错误代码**:\n```python\n# 只处理最后一段\ntotal_move += abs(3600 - valid_positions[-1])\n```\n\n**修复**:\n```python\n# 逐段累加\nfor jump_idx in jump_indices:\n    segment_start = valid_positions[prev_idx]\n    segment_end = valid_positions[jump_idx - 1]\n    total_move += abs(segment_end - segment_start)\n    # 跳变跨越\n    jump_from = valid_positions[jump_idx - 1]\n    jump_to = valid_positions[jump_idx]\n    if jump_to < jump_from:\n        total_move += abs(3600 - jump_from) + abs(jump_to - 0)\n    else:\n        total_move += abs(jump_from - 0) + abs(3600 - jump_to)\n    prev_idx = jump_idx\n# 最后一段\nif prev_idx < len(valid_positions) - 1:\n    total_move += abs(valid_positions[-1] - valid_positions[prev_idx])\n```\n\n**教训**:\n- Pan无限位跳变需要分段计算\n- 每段距离都要累加\n- 不能只处理最后一段\n\n---\n\n## ERR-20260530-005: Tilt翻转检测位置硬编码\n\n**时间**: 2026-05-30 17:22\n**优先级**: MEDIUM\n**状态**: 已修复\n**摘要**: Tilt翻转检测使用固定位置 curr >= 700，应该检测趋势变化\n\n**错误代码**:\n```python\nif curr < prev and curr >= 700:\n    flip_detected = True\n```\n\n**修复**:\n```python\n# 检测趋势变化\nfor i in range(10, len(positions)):\n    recent_trend = sum(positions[j] - positions[j-1] for j in range(i-4, i+1))\n    if movement_dir == \"increasing\" and recent_trend < 0:\n        flip_detected = True\n    elif movement_dir == \"decreasing\" and recent_trend > 0:\n        flip_detected = True\n```\n\n**教训**:\n- 翻转检测基于趋势变化，不是固定位置\n- 递增趋势→递减趋势 = 翻转\n- 递减趋势→递增趋势 = 翻转"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":109939,"output":1164,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111103,"cost":{"input":0.109939,"output":0.0037248000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1136638}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780143798948,"responseId":"cht000d19d1@dx19e78d6bdf4b828282"}}
