{"type":"message","id":"cc5d0f10","parentId":"b3271b0b","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:06:48.343Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**问题发现：**\n\n1. **`ptz.goto_preset(10)` 和 `ptz.wait_stable()` 在测试完成后执行** - 如果测试中途被中断，这行代码不会执行\n2. **`except Exception: pass`** - 如果保存失败，错误被忽略，不会报错\n\n**原因：测试进程被中断，没有执行到后处理和保存 JSON 的代码。**\n\n**流程：**\n```\n采样完成 → post_process_csv → ptz.goto_preset(10) → ptz.wait_stable() → 保存JSON\n```\n\n如果进程在 `post_process_csv` 之后、`ptz.goto_preset(10)` 之前被中断，JSON就不会生成。\n\n**解决方案：**\n- 将 JSON 保存移到 `post_process_csv` 之后立即执行\n- 不要依赖 `goto_preset` 完成后才保存\n\n需要修复吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":126009,"output":187,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126196,"cost":{"input":0.12600899999999998,"output":0.0005984,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.12660739999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780149998999,"responseId":"cht000d1dd3@dx19e793558dcb85f532"}}
