{"type":"message","id":"9056df71","parentId":"f1005133","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:25:24.718Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2a3c0eeda8554103a0ae9ecc","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def post_process_csv(raw_csv_path: str, mac: str, limit_data: dict | None = None) -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\r\n    \"\"\"数据后处理:计算速度。\r\n\r\n    Args:\r\n        raw_csv_path: CSV文件路径\r\n        mac: MAC地址\r\n        limit_data: 限位数据(包含direction_info)\r\n\r\n    计算规则:\r\n    - 取第6-105个点(索引5:105)\r\n    - 速度 = |end - start| / 10.0\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    results = []\r\n\r\n    with open(raw_csv_path, newline=\"\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\r\n        reader = csv.DictReader(f)\r\n        rows = list(reader)\r\n\r\n    # 按组合分组(包含时间戳)\r\n    groups = {}\r\n    for row in rows:\r\n        axis = row.get(\"axis\", \"\").strip()\r\n        direction = int(row.get(\"direction\", 1))\r\n        speed_level = int(row.get(\"speed_level\", 0))\r\n        zoom = int(row.get(\"zoom\", 0))\r\n        repeat_idx = int(row.get(\"repeat_idx\", 0))\r\n        pos = float(row.get(\"position\", 0.0))\r\n        timestamp = row.get(\"timestamp\", \"\")\r\n        key = (axis, direction, speed_level, zoom)\r\n        groups.setdefault(key, []).append({\"position\": pos, \"repeat_idx\": repeat_idx, \"timestamp\": timestamp})\r\n\n[416 more lines in file. Use offset=250 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780151124718}}
{"type":"message","id":"b873c022","parentId":"9056df71","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:25:40.782Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"检查有效点数计算："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-f9f21277ecd74c92adbf6e3e87c6fde4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && python -c \"\nimport csv\n\nwith open('data/iDS-2DF_240f9b764193/20260530_021/speed.csv', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    reader = csv.DictReader(f)\n    rows = list(reader)\n\n# Tilt Speed=100 Zoom=10\nfor direction in ['1', '-1']:\n    print(f'=== Tilt Speed=100 Zoom=10 Direction={direction} ===')\n    data = [r for r in rows if r['axis']=='tilt' and r['direction']==direction and r['speed_level']=='100' and r['zoom']=='10']\n    \n    for repeat in ['0']:\n        points = [r for r in data if r['repeat_idx']==repeat]\n        positions = [float(p['position']) for p in points]\n        \n        # 找到限位点\n        limit_start = -1\n        for i, pos in enumerate(positions):\n            if pos == 900.0 and direction == '1':\n                if i > 0 and positions[i-1] < 900:\n                    limit_start = i\n                    break\n            elif pos == -200.0 and direction == '-1':\n                if i > 0 and positions[i-1] > -200:\n                    limit_start = i\n                    break\n        \n        print(f'  Total points: {len(points)}')\n        print(f'  Limit reached at index: {limit_start}')\n        print(f'  Points before limit: {limit_start}')\n        print(f'  Points at limit (900/-200): {len(points) - limit_start}')\n        \n        # 有效点计算（排除前5点）\n        if limit_start > 5:\n            valid_points = limit_start - 5\n        else:\n            valid_points = limit_start\n        print(f'  Valid points for calc (exclude first 5): {valid_points}')\n    print()\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":53813,"output":440,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,