{"type":"message","id":"c1018917","parentId":"b43a44c1","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:25:50.429Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**回答问题一：到达限位之后的点是否参与计算？**\n\n回答：不参与。限位之后的点被排除。代码检测到限位后，`valid_end = i`，只取到限位前的点。\n\n**回答问题二：到达限位之后有多少个点？**\n\n回答：\n\n| 方向 | 总点数 | 限位开始位置 | 限位前点数 | 限位后点数 |\n|------|--------|--------------|------------|------------|\n| 正向 | 42 | 索引28 | 28 | 14 |\n| 反向 | 48 | 索引28 | 28 | 20 |\n\n不是走完110个点，而是到达限位后立刻停止移动。但采样器还在记录位置（14-20个点都在限位位置）。\n\n**回答问题三：数据不足是什么意思？**\n\n回答：参与计算的数据不足。\n\n| 方向 | 限位前点数 | 排除前5点 | 有效计算点数 |\n|------|------------|-----------|--------------|\n| 正向 | 28 | 5 | **23点** |\n| 反向 | 28 | 5 | **23点** |\n\n**结论：两个方向参与计算的都是23个点，数据量相同。差异来自实际运动时间不同（正向3.7秒，反向4.4秒）。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":54384,"output":292,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54676,"cost":{"input":0.054383999999999995,"output":0.0009344,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0553184}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780151141223,"responseId":"cht000d1c09@dx19e7946c478b8aa822"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2acd1466","parentId":"c1018917","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:31:39.607Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"30250\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-05-30 22:31 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n23个点还不足吗？你现在就用这些23个点给我来手动计算，算一算平均速度是多少。对比刚才你发给我的最终检测的jso报告，看看速度值是否一致"}],"timestamp":1780151499597}}
{"type":"message","id":"8b124a13","parentId":"2acd1466","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:31:57.686Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"手动计算 Speed=100 Zoom=10 的速度："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-723c2d017ebb43be8ca431285b9b06e9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && python -c \"\nimport csv\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nwith open('data/iDS-2DF_240f9b764193/20260530_021/speed.csv', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    reader = csv.DictReader(f)\n    rows = list(reader)\n\nprint('=== Manual Speed Calculation ===')\nprint()\n\nfor direction in ['1', '-1']:\n    print(f'--- Tilt Speed=100 Zoom=10 Direction={direction} ---')\n    data = [r for r in rows if r['axis']=='tilt' and r['direction']==direction and r['speed_level']=='100' and r['zoom']=='10']\n    \n    for repeat in ['0']:\n        points = [r for r in data if r['repeat_idx']==repeat]\n        positions = [float(p['position']) for p in points]\n        timestamps = [p['timestamp'] for p in points]\n        \n        # 找到限位点\n        limit_start = 28\n        \n        # 有效点（排除前5点）\n        valid_start = 5\n        valid_end = limit_start\n        \n        valid_positions = positions[valid_start:valid_end]\n        valid_timestamps = timestamps[valid_start:valid_end]\n        \n        print(f'  Valid points: {len(valid_positions)}')\n        print(f'  First valid position: {valid_positions[0]}')\n        print(f'  Last valid position: {valid_positions[-1]}')\n        print(f'  First valid timestamp: {valid_timestamps[0]}')\n        print(f'  Last valid timestamp: {valid_timestamps[-1]}')\n        \n        # 计算位移\n        displacement = abs(valid_positions[-1] - valid_positions[0])\n        print(f'  Displacement: {displacement}')\n        \n        # 计算时间\n        t_start = datetime.strptime(valid_timestamps[0], '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S.%f')\n        t_end = datetime.strptime(valid_timestamps[-1], '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S.%f')\n        time_sec = (t_end - t_start).total_seconds()\n        print(f'  Time: {time_sec:.3f} seconds')\n        \n        # 计算速度\n        speed = displacement / time_sec\n        print(f'  Speed: {speed:.2f} degrees/sec')\n    print()\n\nprint('=== JSON Report Values ===')\nimport json\nwith open('data/iDS-2DF_240f9b764193/20260530_022/speed.json', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    jdata = json.load(f)\n    for r in jdata['results']:\n        if r['axis']=='tilt' and r['speed_level']==100 and r['zoom']==10:\n            print(f\\\"  Direction={r['direction']}: speed_val={r['speed_val']:.2f}\\\")\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":54872,"output":661,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55533,"cost":{"input":0.054872,"output":0.0021152000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.056987199999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780151499623,"responseId":"cht000d6a44@dx19e794c3e6eb8aa822"}}
