{"type":"message","id":"9db2766a","parentId":"6bfd18b5","timestamp":"2026-05-31T03:38:10.232Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"更新 ERRORS.md："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-5fd0890c3c21400eb283263a1067201d","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"**教训**:\n- 翻转检测基于趋势变化，不是固定位置\n- 递增趋势→递减趋势 = 翻转\n- 递减趋势→递增趋势 = 翻转\n\n---\n\n## ERR-20260531-001: 后处理限位检测逻辑错误\n\n**时间**: 2026-05-31 11:25\n**优先级**: HIGH\n**状态**: 已修复\n**摘要**: 后处理阶段用\"连续20点位置相同且等于限位值\"检测限位，导致正向停在限位14点时未触发\n\n**错误代码**:\n```python\nfor i in range(20, len(positions)):\n    if all(positions[j] == positions[i] for j in range(i-19, i+1)):\n        if positions[i] == tilt_min or positions[i] == tilt_max:\n            valid_end = i - 19\n            break\n```\n\n**修复**:\n```python\nfor i in range(len(positions)):\n    if positions[i] == tilt_min or positions[i] == tilt_max:\n        valid_end = i  # 限位索引\n        limit_detected = True\n        break\n```\n\n**教训**:\n- 采样阶段和后处理阶段是两套逻辑\n- 采样阶段：连续20点位置不变才停止采样\n- 后处理阶段：首次到达限位位置时截断（valid_end=限位索引）\n- 有效点取 positions[5:valid_end]，即索引5到限位前最后一个移动点","oldText":"**教训**:\n- 翻转检测基于趋势变化，不是固定位置\n- 递增趋势→递减趋势 = 翻转\n- 递减趋势→递增趋势 = 翻转"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\.learnings\\ERRORS.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":112283,"output":454,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112737,"cost":{"input":0.112283,"output":0.0014528000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1137358}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780198671816,"responseId":"cht000d1040@dx19e7c1c0852ba29112"}}
