{"type":"message","id":"a634aa2b","parentId":"63cbd1c9","timestamp":"2026-05-31T18:52:13.838Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"更新每日记忆："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-f36bdfa373904fb180ec0e9ee29ac8e6","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 2026-06-01 记忆\n\n## 速度测试修复完成\n\n### 修复项\n1. CSV和JSON写入同一目录（csv_path.with_suffix('.json')）\n2. 后处理限位检测：首次到达限位位置时截断（valid_end=限位索引）\n3. 无翻转/限位时排除后5点（valid_end = len(positions) - 5）\n4. 最小点数从20改为10\n\n### 验证结果\n- Lite档4项检测全部通过\n- 正反向差异 ≤ 5%\n- 速度档位与实际速度一致\n- 低Z值速度 ≥ 高Z值速度\n\n### 关键教训\n- 采样阶段和后处理阶段是两套逻辑\n- 采样阶段：连续20点位置不变才停止采样\n- 后处理阶段：首次到达限位位置时截断\n- 有效点取 positions[5:valid_end]\n\n### 待办\n- 运行Medium档验证","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\memory\\2026-06-01.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":122034,"output":254,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122288,"cost":{"input":0.12203399999999999,"output":0.0008128,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.12284679999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780253522737,"responseId":"cht000d1b0f@dx19e7f610268b87e692"}}
